4. Vera Belcher

# Vera Belcher

## Project Coordinator Web and Mobile Applications

Phone: **512-475-9411** |
Email: **[vbelcher@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:vbelcher@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Vera joined TACC in February 2019 as a Project Coordinator for the Advanced Computing Interfaces team. She provides project management support for Web & Mobile Applications and Cloud & Interactive Computing across a range of programs, including Chameleon and the Bridging Barriers initiatives Whole Communities-Whole Health and Planet Texas 2050. Prior to joining TACC, Vera served as the lead systems administrator for management of the central database for all clinical trial research at The Ohio State University Wexner Medical Center and Comprehensive Cancer Center.

### Education

**B.A., Sociology**  

The Ohio State University